    "g Within the first intron, 233 bp downstream of the expected TSS of Solyc02g080300 epmSoly-M009-p0m04 was identified.",
    "An SV indel mutation of 10 bp lies 7 bp downstream of epmSoly-M009-p0m04, not disrupting the EPM.",
    "In contrast to the example before, the difference between two point mutations coincides with low probabilities of high gene expression for genotypes of variant A within epmSoly-M009-p0m04.",
    "Sopen01g036910; ADC Sopen01g052570, Sopen10g024370; ODC Sopen04g035680; SAMDC Sopen01g005600, Sopen02g034330, Sopen05g006210; CPA Sopen11g027260; SPDS Sopen05g001710; SPMS Sopen03g003220; SSAT Sopen07g002430, Sopen08g002670, Sopen08g002710, Sopen08g022440, Sopen10g034080; PAO2/3/4 Sopen02g026020, Sopen07g023160, Sopen12g002320) and precision for low expression of 0.5 (true negatives obtained for ODC Sopen03g029030, Sopen03g029060; SSAT Sopen12g032670).",
    "Remarkably, despite the high sequence homology to S. lycopersicum, the S. pennellii orthologs showed distinct patterns of gene expression."
